{
  "texts": [
    "This is also confirmed by the experience of getting used to deepCOM before the experiment.",
    "Not only did this rarely take longer than 5 min, but there were generally no questions about the user interface as it was perceived as self-explanatory.",
    "In the personal feedback interviews at the end of the experiment, the participants were also unable to make any suggestions for improving the design of the user interface.",
    "The study identified several challenges in applying AI to the military analysis process; see also Devanny et al. (2023) and Horlings (2023).",
    "For example, the AI search encountered problems when the underlying texts contained no or insufficient information for the answer."
  ]
}